com.bragi.sonify.music

Enum Pitch

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Pitch>
      • com.bragi.sonify.music.Pitch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Pitch>
    Deprecated.

    public enum Pitch
extends java.lang.Enum<Pitch>
    This enum holds constants for three octaves of notes, starting from A3. Every note has its MIDI key number. For a further description of numbering notes in MIDI, refer to * http://computermusicresource.com/midikeys.html
    Author:
    Jan-Christoph Klie
